body.raw: **Hello, I'm Elaine!** I'm a junior at MIT studying Computer Science and Business Analytics. I'm currently based in Cambridge, Massachusetts, but originally from Des Moines, Iowa. My interests lie in the realm of software development, data management, and cloud computing—particularly in finance, entertainment, and emerging tech. I'm passionate about creating and bringing ideas to life, and once I’m into something, I’m *all* in. While I'm not working, I also compete on the Track & Field team, scale new bouldering routes, enjoy reading thought-provoking books, binge-watch action-packed TV shows, and speed-solve all sorts of Rubik's Cubes.
